      "content": "thanks for this. it's okay, but it's a bit too brief. i think we need more detail for the new hires so they don't hit any snags. \n\ncould you expand on it? maybe include what to do if they need to request something urgent or what the approval process looks like. \n\njust a reminder though, try to keep the \"actionability\" score in mind. i need it to be high enough to pass the automated check, but please, don't make it weird or wordy just to get a higher score. keep it helpful and natural.",
